Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:27.46,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}任性的Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:32.13,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒映著的雙眼正看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:48.23,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吶 漂亮不過是外表逞強而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:53.57,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對 就連玫瑰也是帶著刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:58.74,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不是那種受傷也無所謂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:04.58,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}撞到了卻敷衍過去 Pure sign
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.45,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有些地方讓人不耐煩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.00,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又有什麼東西就要溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:12.08,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Please don't please wait
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:15.75,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我明明想大聲喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:17.84,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}任性的Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:22.05,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒映著的純情在搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:26.47,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}另一邊映出的彷彿是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.39,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就算這樣也是Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:32.27,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比起防守 我的行動更注重進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.32,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比精美的玻璃還要脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.11,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:39.49,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.65,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以強制執行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:45.91,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}希望你能看著一個完整的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:51.21,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}裝作從容地接納下我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:54.38,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}害羞的男孩
